docs/RESUME.md

# Results: ignore individual timestamped run dirs — keep aggregated analysis
# + one canonical snapshot tracked explicitly (force-add when ready)
results/run_*/

# Canonical run dir is published (force-added) for reproducibility, EXCEPT
# deblinding maps and aborted-attempt debris — keep these out of the public
# repo regardless of force-add.
results/**/annotation_key.csv
results/**/claude_crossrating_key.csv
results/**/*.aborted

